# Community Hub — serve the Railway app under dabzaudio.com/community-hub
# (keeps the address bar on our domain; hub API calls go direct to Railway, CORS *)
# Proxy rule MUST come first: Netlify normalizes trailing slashes, so a
# "/community-hub -> /community-hub/" redirect would also catch "/community-hub/"
# and loop. Matching the proxy first means the slashed URL is served directly.
/community-hub/*  https://dabzaudio-production.up.railway.app/:splat  200
/community-hub    /community-hub/  301
